"msg":"<blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b825b380784ac3825a5ff009c1025b2df471d0","tid":56144,"uid":7155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56527b19621e30f4c9d33ace42719b5740eeb42f","tid":56144,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟住又講日本唔道歉,唔係一早道左咩,又有資助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d2971272d357192367bb51b2f5aa8de536bea8","tid":56144,"uid":29544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我一路都唔明中國點解會做到常任理事國"},{"pid":"30fae0c360542ff390a85b764576559eb9d5ecf2","tid":56144,"uid":53014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我一路都唔明中國點解會做到常任理事國</blockquote><br />\n因為打果個係中華民國而非支共"},{"pid":"5dc46c6e530351447dfd87cf04d0e597c88befe6","tid":56144,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國一早大勢已去，沿海所有工商業重鎮一早俾日本仔攻佔晒<br />\n<br />\n睇歷史書d版圖，國民黨係仲有好多呀，不過全部都係荒山野嶺"},{"pid":"ef0b9b58c4ab775071cf39afc4e61a90779bca01","tid":56144,"uid":29544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我一路都唔明中國點解會做到常任理事國</blockquote><br />\n因為打果個係中華民國而非支共</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中華民國都係咁話啦<br />\n嗰陣國民黨畀日本打到要縮上山喎<br />\n唔係蘇聯同美國幫拖嘅話佢遲早全軍覆沒"},{"pid":"b5cca1ea0b83780a48433bc195db2f4513e64ad8","tid":56144,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知同好奇一問<br />\n咁真正投原子彈原因係咩？</blockquote><br />\n實驗<br />\n當時只係試爆咗第一粒，第二粒第三粒已經係射去日本試下威力"},{"pid":"f0fac5b329e4cc57c2d53e1cca17688183b7649c","tid":56144,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"我都係廢老。其實讀近代史或現代史絕對不用也不要讀國民黨或老共的官方認可著作。一定要學好英文，看西方的史料。Internet及Youtube有大量免費資料。"},{"pid":"a224ce717af83921b386a1b1031ffb937ffea1d1","tid":56144,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無西方盟軍幫拖，中國都無埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國一早大勢已去，沿海所有工商業重鎮一早俾日本仔攻佔晒<br />\n<br />\n睇歷史書d版圖，國民黨係仲有好多呀，不過全部都係荒山野嶺</blockquote><br />\n其實可以話二戰日本是敗在自己手上。如果以做生意比喻，日本仔的死因就是過度擴張。偷襲珍珠港挑起的太平洋戰爭是The beginning of the end。"},{"pid":"2a702fc3cd78974e13a63798adfd31fca3f0a7be","tid":56144,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係廢老。其實讀近代史或現代史絕對不用也不要讀國民黨或老共的官方認可著作。一定要學好英文，看西方的史料。Internet及Youtube有大量免費資料。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢老上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1020911e9b55b1f99b408f9bdc7de82d3683ebf","tid":56144,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日講到美國係最邪惡 中國就係最弱勢最和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017都黎緊，但仲講緊8年抗戰共產黨點屈日本仔機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br